title: Marvel's Warlock, 60s-70s, digital rips only.
description:
Classic early tales of Adam Warlock from the 1960s and 70s.

From his first appearance as the genetically engineered creature, Him, Adam Warlock found his name and dark purpose. 

This torrent includes the Magus Saga, one of the best sci fi series of the 70s. Jim Starlin crafted a complex character who was both hero and villain, layered with religious overtones.

This compilation includes Fantastic Four 66-67, The Mighty Thor 165-166, The Power of Warlock TPB, Strange Tales 178-181, Warlock 9-15, Marvel Team-Up 55, Avengers Annual 7 and Marvel Two-in-One Annual 2.

All digital rips, credit to all rippers. I've only compiled their work
